name: The Signal
overview: A missing astronaut sets her family on a frantic hunt for answers. But the more they uncover, the greater the threat becomes to them — and the world.

episodes.name: Vanished
episodes.overview: Astronaut Paula is on her way back from a mission. Her husband Sven and daughter Charlie are excited to see her when they receive upsetting news.

episodes.name: Paula
episodes.overview: In space, Paula starts to question herself as the weight of her discovery sinks in. Sven and Charlie deal with the fallout of the accident.

episodes.name: Black Box
episodes.overview: Sven faces new threats and makes unexpected allies in his search for the truth. Paula deals with a traitor during a critical phase of her mission.

episodes.name: Departure
episodes.overview: Forced to evade a powerful enemy, Sven puts his faith in Charlie as they try to solve the final piece of Paula's puzzle.
